      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "でも、琴乃ちゃんはライブに誘っても\n行きたくないって言ってるんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Kotono-chan says she doesn't want to go\nto your lives.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 327.6000261933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs021.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんが嫌がってるのなら\n無理強いはしたくありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Kotono-chan doesn't want to go‚\nI don't want to force her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 333.8333595266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs022.m4a",
      "text": "……だけど、もしも琴乃ちゃんが\n麻奈さんと仲直りしたいって言ったら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But if Kotono-chan\nsays she wants to make up with you‚ Mana-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 339.7999916066,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs023.m4a",
      "text": "その時は、麻奈さんのライブに誘います\nそうすることが琴乃ちゃんのためだと思うから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "then I'll invite her to your live.\nBecause I think that's what's best for her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 347.0333086639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_thanks-04.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、今はそれで十分だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ that's enough for now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 351.1598231854,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "二人がライブに来てくれるのを待ってるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll be waiting for you both to come to my live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 356.3931851028,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……渚ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Nagisa-chan‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 361.6265325767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-12.m4a",
      "text": "これからもずっと、琴乃の味方でいてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "please stay by Kotono's side.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 364.3598450564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_04_02-ngs024.m4a",
      "text": "はい。約束します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I promise.",
        "id": ""
      },
